{"title":"再下思茅坝","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1962,"month":1,"day":14}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"再下思茅坝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“要下思茅坝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"先把老婆嫁。”〔注〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"民谣传西南，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瘴气人人怕。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瘴气是恶疟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杀人如割麻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"古称瘴疠地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新名高疟区。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谷子地里熟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人却病在家。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"历代反动派，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喝血如喝茶。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不顾人死活，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无医又无药。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杀牛祭鬼神，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有鬼名“琵琶”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"病人不得活，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"活人遭惨杀。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地广人烟稀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"豹子闯县衙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"边疆解放后，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"起了大变化。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"政策改造了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十二个版纳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一把迷信破，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二把蚊蝇打。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"防疫进深山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"求医下平坝。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开办训练班，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"傣族出摩雅，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红十字背包，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘肩头挎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大妈下竹楼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"握手将她夸："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“年年打摆子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今年不再发。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"感谢毛主席！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我把像片挂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“家家都清健，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从古没有啊！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四邻都赞成"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大妈一番话。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千古瘴疠地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开遍幸福花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再下思茅坝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁能认识它？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"10月末，思茅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瘴疠［zhàng-lì］"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔注〕西双版纳等地是历史上有名的“瘴气”区域，所谓瘴气，即恶性疟疾。景洪坝和橄榄坝，更被称为“瘴气的母地”或“高疟区”。云南过去流行着两句民谣：“要下思茅坝，先把老婆嫁。”解放后大搞爱国卫生运动，疟疾发病率大大降低，培养了傣族的医生、卫生员（傣语叫做“摩雅傣”），打破了“琵琶鬼”等迷信。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":5,"page_end":5}